function.arguments:
{"command":"create","path":"/workspace/system_cleanup.sh","file_text":"#!/bin/bash
# This script will perform system cleanup tasks

# Clear system cache
sudo sync; echo 3 > /proc/sys/vm/drop_caches

# Remove unused packages
sudo apt-get autoremove -y

# Clean up package cache
sudo apt-get clean

# Remove old log files
sudo find /var/log -type f -name "*.log" -mtime +7 -exec rm -f {} \;

# Remove temporary files
sudo rm -rf /tmp/*

# Display disk usage
sudo df -h
"}
